WEBVTT

00:00:00.033 --> 00:00:45.125
Subtitle Provide by dramacool.in Translator [Admin.@YNG]

00:00:54.833 --> 00:00:56.125
Alright, don't be afraid.

00:00:58.083 --> 00:00:59.583
As far as I know,

00:00:59.666 --> 00:01:02.416
Teng Rong died around 9 to 11 pm last night.

00:01:02.666 --> 00:01:04.541
What were you two doing at that time? Please tell me.

00:01:04.583 --> 00:01:05.791
Young Hero Lin,

00:01:06.416 --> 00:01:08.083
My wife was just frightened.

00:01:08.333 --> 00:01:09.833
Could you speak more gently?

00:01:10.208 --> 00:01:11.458
It's alright, my dear.

00:01:11.583 --> 00:01:13.583
Young Hero Lin is just doing his duty.

00:01:14.625 --> 00:01:15.666
It's fine.

00:01:18.333 --> 00:01:19.708
Last night...

00:01:19.916 --> 00:01:21.375
I was taking a bath.

00:01:24.625 --> 00:01:25.916
Unexpectedly,

00:01:26.291 --> 00:01:27.583
Teng Rong barged in.

00:01:27.666 --> 00:01:28.750
Senior Sister,

00:01:31.208 --> 00:01:32.083
Madam,

00:01:32.416 --> 00:01:33.458
Madam,

00:01:37.125 --> 00:01:38.375
What's wrong, Madam?

00:01:38.500 --> 00:01:40.291
Dear, Teng Rong...

00:01:40.541 --> 00:01:42.250
Teng Rong was peeking at me while I bathed.

00:01:42.333 --> 00:01:43.916
He peeked at you bathing?

00:01:44.041 --> 00:01:45.708
That bastard Teng Rong!

00:01:48.166 --> 00:01:50.958
Are you sure it was Teng Rong who peeked at you last night?

00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:53.750
Yes, though the lighting was dim that night.

00:01:54.041 --> 00:01:56.583
My husband chased after him and caught him quickly.

00:01:57.083 --> 00:01:58.083
That's right.

00:01:58.333 --> 00:01:59.375
Last night...

00:02:00.708 --> 00:02:01.583
Stop!

00:02:02.458 --> 00:02:02.958
Second Brother,

00:02:03.041 --> 00:02:04.375
Teng Rong, you bastard!

00:02:04.958 --> 00:02:07.541
How dare you do such a vile thing to your Senior Sister!

00:02:07.833 --> 00:02:08.833
Lian Songbai,

00:02:09.041 --> 00:02:11.000
Don't think you can bully me just because you have the Lian family behind you.

00:02:11.041 --> 00:02:12.083
That gives you no right to insult me.

00:02:12.166 --> 00:02:14.000
I'm now Lord Gao's adopted son.

00:02:14.125 --> 00:02:15.416
My status is no less than yours.

00:02:15.416 --> 00:02:17.916
Don't think I don't know your relationship with Lord Gao.

00:02:18.041 --> 00:02:20.166
You're just someone he keeps for his own amusement.

00:02:20.208 --> 00:02:21.083
You...

00:02:24.458 --> 00:02:28.500
So Teng Rong's claim of being an official's adopted son was all made up.

00:02:28.583 --> 00:02:29.500
That's right.

00:02:32.791 --> 00:02:34.791
Then do you know why your junior Teng Rong

00:02:34.833 --> 00:02:36.541
was worshipping a corpse?

00:02:36.958 --> 00:02:38.125
What?

00:02:38.375 --> 00:02:40.291
He was worshipping a corpse?

00:02:55.625 --> 00:02:57.500
It's time for you to speak, Young Master Gao.

00:02:57.750 --> 00:02:59.000
Around 9 to 11 pm last night,

00:02:59.041 --> 00:03:00.458
what exactly were you doing?

00:03:03.333 --> 00:03:05.583
This is my manor's unique tea brewing technique.

00:03:05.625 --> 00:03:07.500
Most people don't understand its subtleties.

00:03:08.250 --> 00:03:09.500
Young Hero Lin, have a taste.

00:03:11.500 --> 00:03:13.166
You've been using tea to dodge questions.

00:03:13.250 --> 00:03:15.833
Could it be that you're the ghost?

00:03:16.708 --> 00:03:17.625
How crude.

00:03:17.666 --> 00:03:19.000
Where were you before the incident?

00:03:19.583 --> 00:03:21.958
Last night, I was playing chess with my master in the room.

00:03:22.041 --> 00:03:23.625
We played until midnight before leaving.

00:03:23.666 --> 00:03:24.916
Who won?

00:03:25.250 --> 00:03:27.833
Three games, I lost every one.

00:03:28.833 --> 00:03:30.458
But losing to my master

00:03:30.583 --> 00:03:32.125
is an honor for me.

00:03:43.083 --> 00:03:45.416
Everyone is hiding something.

00:03:47.416 --> 00:03:49.750
Who really killed you?

00:04:03.958 --> 00:04:06.541
What happened today is truly strange.

00:04:06.625 --> 00:04:10.916
Young Hero Lin, are you trying to get information from me?

00:04:13.916 --> 00:04:15.708
A ghost taps your shoulder,

00:04:15.916 --> 00:04:17.458
your days are numbered.

00:04:17.541 --> 00:04:18.416
Darn it.

00:04:18.541 --> 00:04:20.916
How could Steward Wang...

00:04:35.791 --> 00:04:37.500
Master! Master! Master!

00:04:45.000 --> 00:04:48.291
He's been with me for over ten years.

00:04:49.333 --> 00:04:51.000
Master, Manor Lord, Master!

00:04:51.458 --> 00:04:53.208
Help the Manor Lord back to rest first.

00:04:53.416 --> 00:04:54.416
Alright.

00:04:55.541 --> 00:04:57.666
Young Master Gao, I have something to ask you.

00:05:03.958 --> 00:05:05.083
Speak plainly.

00:05:07.041 --> 00:05:09.041
Actually, I just asked the Manor Lord.

00:05:10.083 --> 00:05:14.333
He said you won two games and lost one yesterday.

00:05:15.708 --> 00:05:17.708
Did you not get your stories straight, or...

00:05:17.791 --> 00:05:19.541
Then I want to ask you instead.

00:05:20.125 --> 00:05:22.583
Why did you rush to send Master away just now?

00:05:23.708 --> 00:05:25.708
Instead of letting the three of us confront each other?

00:05:27.333 --> 00:05:28.291
As for me,

00:05:28.833 --> 00:05:30.500
I know Master's character well.

00:05:30.958 --> 00:05:33.333
He values the manor's reputation above all.

00:05:34.291 --> 00:05:35.916
Now that someone has died here,

00:05:36.250 --> 00:05:39.041
he would never let an outsider interfere.

00:05:42.125 --> 00:05:43.333
Young Master Gao,

00:05:45.666 --> 00:05:46.958
Aren't you afraid

00:05:47.708 --> 00:05:48.916
you'll be next?

00:05:51.333 --> 00:05:53.708
My conscience is clear; I fear nothing.

00:05:54.458 --> 00:05:56.666
You should worry about yourself.

00:06:08.041 --> 00:06:09.166
Charming

00:06:10.083 --> 00:06:11.625
Truly charming

00:06:14.708 --> 00:06:15.791
Husband

00:06:18.583 --> 00:06:19.791
I'm scared

00:06:23.083 --> 00:06:24.333
Don't be afraid, my lady

00:06:24.625 --> 00:06:26.500
Whether the killer is human or ghost

00:06:26.666 --> 00:06:27.916
if they want to harm you

00:06:28.375 --> 00:06:30.041
they'll have to get past me first

00:06:30.208 --> 00:06:31.958
Don't say that, husband

00:06:32.916 --> 00:06:34.625
I know you care about me

00:06:35.250 --> 00:06:36.916
But you must be careful too

00:06:37.000 --> 00:06:38.250
Don't worry, my lady

00:06:38.625 --> 00:06:39.833
You should rest first

00:06:40.000 --> 00:06:41.125
I'll go find Master

00:06:41.250 --> 00:06:42.041
Alright

00:07:01.750 --> 00:07:02.791
Darling

00:07:04.875 --> 00:07:06.083
You're annoying

00:07:06.625 --> 00:07:08.000
Look at the situation we're in

00:07:08.333 --> 00:07:09.916
And you still think about this

00:07:10.041 --> 00:07:11.625
Oh, what are you afraid of

00:07:11.750 --> 00:07:13.125
At times like this

00:07:14.291 --> 00:07:16.083
you're the most tempting

00:07:19.666 --> 00:07:20.708
Senior Brother

00:07:20.750 --> 00:07:21.416
Yes

00:07:21.791 --> 00:07:23.166
Let's run away

00:07:24.875 --> 00:07:26.291
I keep feeling

00:07:26.708 --> 00:07:28.583
this is aimed at the two of us

00:07:29.125 --> 00:07:30.500
Our affair

00:07:30.708 --> 00:07:33.000
If my husband finds out

00:07:34.041 --> 00:07:36.958
So we should just escape together

00:07:37.583 --> 00:07:38.666
Escape?

00:07:39.375 --> 00:07:40.833
Why should I run away

00:07:41.833 --> 00:07:44.625
Lian Songbai inherited the Lian family business

00:07:45.250 --> 00:07:47.500
Now there's a vengeful spirit killing people

00:07:47.958 --> 00:07:50.833
I can use the spirit to kill him

00:07:51.708 --> 00:07:53.875
Then we can be together, just the two of us

00:07:53.916 --> 00:07:55.666
Isn't that the perfect plan

00:07:55.833 --> 00:07:57.833
You want to kill Lian Songbai

00:08:00.083 --> 00:08:02.458
Of course I don't want to dirty my own hands

00:08:03.291 --> 00:08:05.416
I'll let the spirit do it

00:08:06.708 --> 00:08:07.708
Besides

00:08:08.291 --> 00:08:09.791
With you as my witness

00:08:10.416 --> 00:08:11.500
What do I have to fear

00:08:13.541 --> 00:08:16.541
My husband is your junior brother after all

00:08:17.458 --> 00:08:18.916
You really are ruthless

00:08:19.000 --> 00:08:19.875
What's wrong

00:08:20.333 --> 00:08:23.583
You act like a witch and still pretend to be virtuous

00:08:25.583 --> 00:08:26.583
Let me tell you

00:08:27.041 --> 00:08:28.750
Even if we run away

00:08:29.291 --> 00:08:32.166
How could a poor scholar like me support you

00:08:32.833 --> 00:08:34.541
I'm doing all this for us

00:08:34.833 --> 00:08:36.333
It's all for us

00:08:36.541 --> 00:08:38.041
Let go of me

00:08:43.375 --> 00:08:44.416
Stay away from me

00:08:44.458 --> 00:08:46.333
You're not doing this for us at all

00:08:46.625 --> 00:08:48.583
You just want the Lian family fortune

00:08:48.750 --> 00:08:50.791
Gao Li, you're a scoundrel

00:08:50.916 --> 00:08:53.500
You filthy witch, don't know what's good for you, do you

00:09:02.666 --> 00:09:03.583
Gao Li

00:09:07.291 --> 00:09:09.250
I never thought you, so well-dressed

00:09:09.333 --> 00:09:11.458
would be a scoundrel stealing another's wife

00:09:11.500 --> 00:09:12.541
Husband, save me

00:09:12.583 --> 00:09:13.541
Junior Brother Lian

00:09:14.166 --> 00:09:15.750
Why ruin our brotherhood over a woman

00:09:16.083 --> 00:09:18.291
and destroy our bond

00:09:19.541 --> 00:09:22.750
My lady, have you treated me fairly

00:09:22.750 --> 00:09:24.500
No, it's not like that

00:09:24.666 --> 00:09:26.250
It was him, Gao Li

00:09:26.458 --> 00:09:27.708
He's a scoundrel

00:09:27.791 --> 00:09:29.541
He not only covets the Lian family fortune

00:09:30.125 --> 00:09:31.500
he also forced me

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:33.416
If I didn't obey him

00:09:33.958 --> 00:09:35.875
he would kill both of us

00:09:36.750 --> 00:09:38.625
You filthy witch, you're slandering me

00:09:38.958 --> 00:09:40.000
Gao Li

00:09:40.208 --> 00:09:43.541
Only today have I truly seen your true face

00:09:44.083 --> 00:09:47.125
Bastard, I'll kill you

00:09:47.250 --> 00:09:48.333
Stop

00:09:48.916 --> 00:09:50.708
Everyone, stop

00:09:52.625 --> 00:09:54.583
I said stop

00:09:57.958 --> 00:09:59.083
This room is filthy

00:09:59.208 --> 00:10:01.083
So filthy

00:10:02.916 --> 00:10:06.291
Gao Li, you are all vile and base

00:10:06.375 --> 00:10:09.875
How can you still call yourself my disciple, Ouyang Ming's disciple

00:10:11.750 --> 00:10:15.583
Last night, I played chess with you until midnight

00:10:15.708 --> 00:10:18.208
I thought you were upright

00:10:18.541 --> 00:10:22.458
But I never expected you to do such disgraceful things

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:23.791
Last night, I clearly

00:10:23.791 --> 00:10:27.750
Last night, Wang Zheng mentioned you and He Yun

00:10:27.958 --> 00:10:30.708
I even told him not to speak nonsense

00:10:30.708 --> 00:10:31.375
But

00:10:31.875 --> 00:10:33.166
I never expected

00:10:33.291 --> 00:10:36.083
You really are a hypocrite

00:10:36.916 --> 00:10:38.791
Even your junior brother's wife

00:10:38.833 --> 00:10:41.291
You dare to touch her

00:10:43.708 --> 00:10:44.625
Manor Lord

00:10:44.750 --> 00:10:46.000
Anger harms the body, anger harms the body

00:10:46.000 --> 00:10:47.625
I'll deal with you later

00:10:52.041 --> 00:10:53.083
Husband

00:11:00.750 --> 00:11:03.416
I have lived my life with integrity.

00:11:03.708 --> 00:11:06.208
All I ever wanted was for this Manor,

00:11:06.666 --> 00:11:11.250
to be a pure land for scholars and poets.

00:11:13.583 --> 00:11:15.541
But now, I never expected

00:11:16.666 --> 00:11:18.625
that my own disciples

00:11:18.875 --> 00:11:21.958
would turn out to be such scoundrels.

00:11:24.125 --> 00:11:25.250
Manor Lord,

00:11:27.083 --> 00:11:28.583
what are you really hiding?

00:11:30.875 --> 00:11:32.583
Including the unidentified body at the birthday banquet,

00:11:32.625 --> 00:11:34.500
there are now three deaths in total.

00:11:34.875 --> 00:11:35.791
If this continues,

00:11:35.875 --> 00:11:38.333
this Manor may soon become a place haunted by vengeful spirits.

00:11:39.208 --> 00:11:40.791
Do not speak nonsense.

00:11:41.125 --> 00:11:45.333
This Manor is a pure land away from the world.

00:11:46.208 --> 00:11:48.458
How could there be vengeful ghosts here?

00:11:53.500 --> 00:11:55.208
A pure land away from the world?

00:12:06.875 --> 00:12:08.000
Young Master Gao,

00:12:08.708 --> 00:12:10.625
even your master no longer protects you.

00:12:10.750 --> 00:12:12.375
Will you still keep hiding the truth?